	(text_box "The LMR51450SDRRR is a drop in replacement that will increase efficiency slightly, for 5V this means about 3% improvement during USB charging to about 20% while not, no consequence other than bom consolidation. More importantly, the swap will increase 9V rail efficiency during radio recieve by about 20%, but spread spectrum switching may significantly increase receiver noise, test to investigate."
